Program: Discovery
Title: Metal Mickey comes of age
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p03jrxtj
Last Broadcast Date: 16 May 2001
The programme looks at the debate over artificial intelligence, and what it is. Alan Turing said the test would be that if a computer cannot be told apart from a human in a text conversation, then regardless of soul or conscience, that machine exhibits intelligent behaviour. Scientists debate how relevant this rule is now. Show less